{"questionId":"27856","questionHtml":"<p>Show that the cost per hour for Yvonne is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>NOK&nbsp;312</mtext></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>recognition of need to integrate (e.g. reverse power rule or integral symbol)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>980</mn><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>328</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>980</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><br><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em> for substitution of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>328</mn></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math> into their <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced></math>. A constant of integration must be seen (can be implied by a correct answer).</p>\n<p><br><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>32</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mfenced><mn>7</mn></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>980</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mn>32</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs